    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> in 700ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[1.1L]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
